This file contains bidirectional Unicode text that may be interpreted or compiled differently than what appears below. To review, open the file in an editor that reveals hidden Unicode characters. Learn more about bidirectional Unicode characters







        Suggested change











                border: 2px solid #8be9ff;



                border: 2px solid #4dc6e1;






This looks good, now we just need to readjust to a bolder color, to compensate for illusion of darkness because of only a few pixels being displayed (a line) instead of a larger swath of color (a full background).

